column5: I'm sure that this is a simple solution.............. bear in mind I am very technically challenged. I have a new laptop running Windows 7. When I am logged into OFC and click to a new page I get thrown out and have to log in again......next page same thing..............
Did you forget to mail your cheque John? I haven't received anything yet.
Have you got the new Internet Exploder with that?
It's in the mail Roy.............dang postal workers......
Knew you mods would eventually catch up to me.........
I'm real tempted to break it in for you.
Carol told me to do it
Do I remember a little conversation that went something like......."what happens at Lakair,stays at Lakair"..........things are becoming all fuzzy, can't remember what I said to who now.............
Hey now John...This isn't a Lakair related issue
Bettys laptop has been doing the same thing. Not only on OFC.
